<br>
However, I do not think said item would prevent the casting of the spell if you were out of mana. Your <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Bracer of Restoration</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->(example) probably &quot;would begin to glow&quot; even if you were OOM and it would likely still heal the target and <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> try</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> to take mana from you, draining whatever you had left, but not prevent the click.<br>
